contains.display: ELECTRODES BLUE SENSOR DISP WET GEL
Contains Main Kit, Accessory Kit, and Nonin Pulse Oximeter, USA only
Contains BresoSensor Frame (50 units) and BresoTape (100 Units); USA only
Contains BresoHub and BresoSensor; USA Only
Oximeter Medical Tape Strip is used to maintain the proper placement of the Oximeter Reusable Soft Sensor on the finger. In every pack, there are 100 strips.

BresoSensor Frame is a biocompatible component. BresoSensor Frame is a plastic holder with a medical grade adhesive on the patientâ€™s contact side. BresoSensor Frame is used to hold BresoSensor on the suprasternal notch. During a test, BresoSensor Frame is intended to be in contact with the patientâ€™s skin for a maximum period of 8 hours.

BresoSensor is a component of BresoDX1. During a test, BresoSensor is placed on the suprasternal notch of a patient and collects the tracheal sound and tracheo-sternal motion through a microphone and three-dimensional accelerometer. The BresoSensor is powered by an internal Lithium-ion rechargeable battery. It is only sold in USA.

BresoHub is a component of BresoDX1. During a test, BresoHub is placed at the patientâ€™s bedside to receive the data from BresoSensor and the pulse oximeter wirelessly, and it stores the data locally. BresoHub is powered by a provided power supply.  This device is only sold USA.
